Package edu.monash.fit2099.game.items

This module is about the items that can be used/seen within the edu.monash.fit2099.game.

This module explores the different items that can be used in this edu.monash.fit2099.game. Note that Wallet class does not extend item abstract class from engine package, while the other items in this package do. Thus, the reason why Wallet is here is because it still represents an item, just that Wallet is not used like how an item is used in this particular edu.monash.fit2099.game (allows player to have capabilities/provides actions to actor).
